<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٤٠:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {أَزِفَتِ الْآزِفَةُ <span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> لَيْسَ لَهَا مِنْ دُونِ اللَّهِ كَاشِفَةٌ <span class="c2">(٥٨)</span> أَفَمِنْ هَذَا الْحَدِيثِ تَعْجَبُونَ <span class="c2">(٥٩)</span> وَتَضْحَكُونَ وَلَا تَبْكُونَ <span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> وَأَنْتُمْ سَامِدُونَ <span class="c2">(٦١)</span>} <span class="c4">[النجم: ٥٧ - ٦١]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{أَزِفَتْ الآزِفَةُ}</span>: <span class="c2">«اقْتَرَبَتِ السَّاعَةُ»</span>،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{سَامِدُونَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«البَرْطَمَةُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عِكْرِمَةُ:</span> <span class="c2">«يَتَغَنَّوْنَ، بِالحِمْيَرِيَّةِ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>